700265f-a.title: Bronx: 180th Street (West) - Loring Place
700265f-a.text:
W. 180th Street, north side, between Loring and Osborne Places,
showing the Mrs. C. E. Schwab house(1828) on the Tew York
University grounds. It isthe site of Fort No. 8 in the
Revolution, according to Kr. Chrystie.
E. P. Chrystie  July 7, 1923
